title: CrackBeats.25.apk
description: CrackBeats is the ultimate source for streaming and downloading the latest Hip-Hop, R&B, and Rap Beats! Has a nice interface, view thumbnails of the artists. First stream and decide if you want to download to MP3 format. I have used this App and it works. A must have if you have rhyming skillz! One last thing, these tracks are instrumentals...that means no lyrics from the artists. Enjoy and re-seed please!
